<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SmartLock™ Channel System</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #fff;
      color: #3b4a5e;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    @media (min-width: 992px) {
      .container {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }
    }

    /* Header / breadcrumbs */
    .breadcrumbs {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #b37a28;
    }

    .breadcrumbs span {
      display: inline-block;
    }

    /* Product title */
    .content h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: #141b2d;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .content p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 600px;
    }
details {
  border: 1px solid #dfe4ea;
  border-radius: 6px;
  position: relative;
  background: #f5f7fa;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* summary */
summary {
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  cursor: pointer;
  padding: 14px 16px;
  position: relative;
  list-style: none;
}

/* remove default arrow */
summary::-webkit-details-marker {
  display: block;
}

summary::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  right: 16px;
  top: 50%;
  width: 10px;
  height: 10px;
  border-right: 2px solid #141b2d;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #141b2d;
  transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(45deg); /* down arrow */
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

/* jab open ho */
details[open] summary::after {
  transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(-135deg); /* up arrow */
}


details[open] > *:not(summary) {
  width: 100%;
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid #dfe4ea;
  z-index: 10;
  border-radius: 6px;
}

/* when open */
details[open] > *:not(summary) {
  padding: auto;
  height: max-content; /* adjust if needed */
}

    .btn {
      padding: 14px 24px;
      background: #141b2d;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      opacity: 0.85;
    }

    /* Image styling */
    .image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content">
      <div class="breadcrumbs">
        <span style="color: black;">← ALL SYSTEMS</span>
        <span style="font-size: 14px;">Balustrade & Pool</span>
      </div>

      <h1>SmartLock™ Channel System</h1>
      <p>
        The Opus SmartLock™ Channel System is a premium frameless glass solution designed for easy installation and sleek aesthetics. 
        It suits glass thicknesses from 12mm to 21.52mm and can be top or side fixed into timber, steel, or concrete.
      </p>

      <details>
        <summary>Scope of Use</summary>
       <ul>
        <li>Suitable for balustrades, pool fencing, wind breaks, or barriers</li>
        <li>Suitable for residential and commercial applications</li>

       </ul>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>Windzone</summary>
        <p>Engineered for wind zones up to N3/C1 when installed to specification. Consult engineering documentation for site-specific requirements.</p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>Limitations</summary>
        <p>Not suitable for structural load-bearing applications. Maximum panel width restrictions apply based on glass thickness and wind zone rating.</p>
      </details>

      <button class="btn">Shop SmartLock™</button>
    </div>

    <div class="image">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600607687939-ce8a6c25118c?w=800&q=80" alt="SmartLock Channel System">
    </div>
  </div>
  </body>
</html>


{% schema %}
